David Hembrow is a Dutch cycling advocate who resides in Assen, Netherlands. In his English-language blog, A View from the Cycle Path, he describes how the Dutch cycling infrastructure works, how it has become the best in the world, and how this infrastructure encourages the Netherlands to have highest level of cycling mode share in the world. His blog has become quite influential in the world of cycling advocacy.
